---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHead from '../components/PageHead.astro';
import Pillar from '../components/Pillar.astro';
import CTABand from '../components/CTABand.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Octopad | Human-AI symbiosis for small teams"
  description="Why we built Octopad: a shared back-office where humans set direction and AI handles the structured work. Strategy, tasks, and knowledge every AI can read."
  page="about"
>
  <PageHead
    kicker="About"
    heading="The back-office <br/>your AI has been missing."
    lede="Octopad is where your strategy, tasks, and team knowledge live together. One structured environment every AI your team uses (Claude, ChatGPT, Cursor) can read, update, and run the work from."
  />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <Pillar>
        <Fragment slot="copy">
          <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-green">Our vision</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">A future where humans and AI work together, naturally.</h2>
        </Fragment>
        <div>
          <p class="copy">
            The next decade of work is humans and AI in the same workspace, sharing the same context and the same source of truth, each doing what it does best.
          </p>
          <p class="copy" style="margin-top: 16px;">
            AI today isn't ready to run impactful work alone, and that's fine. The win is symbiosis: you set direction and make the calls, your AI handles the structured work underneath. As agents mature, they'll extend that foundation, not replace the humans at the center.
          </p>
        </div>
      </Pillar>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <Pillar reverse>
        <Fragment slot="copy">
          <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-green">Our mission</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Build the back-office where humans and AI work together as partners.</h2>
        </Fragment>
        <div>
          <p class="copy">
            One back-office where strategy, tasks, and team knowledge live together. A single source of truth every AI your team uses can read and update.
          </p>
        </div>
      </Pillar>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <Pillar>
        <Fragment slot="copy">
          <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-green">Where we're going</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Where we're going.</h2>
        </Fragment>
        <div>
          <p class="copy">
            First, the fundamentals: context that travels with the work, plans that hold across sessions, a shared source of truth that stays current as things change.
          </p>
          <p class="copy" style="margin-top: 16px;">
            Next, proactive agents woven into the system itself, noticing slipping deadlines, flagging stale decisions, keeping plans current without a human pushing every button.
          </p>
          <p class="copy" style="margin-top: 16px;">
            Then, agent delegation. You brainstorm a plan with one AI, then hand individual steps to specialized agents. Each picks up with the full back-office context, runs its part, and reports back. You keep the strategy and the final call.
          </p>
        </div>
      </Pillar>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABand
    heading="Try the back-office your AI has been missing."
    description="Free to start. No credit card. Connect your AI in minutes."
  >
    <a href="https://www.octopad.app/signup" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Create your workspace</a>
  </CTABand>
</BaseLayout>
